OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and showers, some heavy, during
OL,7,Fthe evening. Clear spells increase as
OL,8,Fshowers die from late evening but
OL,9,Fcloud and rain spread northeast
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FEarly cloud and rain soon
OL,13,Fclear northeast to leave the morning
OL,14,Fdry with sunny spells. The odd shower
OL,15,Fwill develop during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
