OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FDry at
OL,6,Ffirst Saturday, cloud, rain soon push
OL,7,Fnortheast. A band of rain pushes east
OL,8,Fon Sunday, drier in northeast. Rain
OL,9,Fclears early Monday, mostly dry, sunny
OL,10,Fin the afternoon.
